        SET_SHOWN_HIDDEN_TABS: function (t) {
          (t.shownTabs = []), (t.hiddenTabs = []);
          var e,
            n = 0;
          for (e = 0; e < t.tabs.length; e++) {
            var r = t.tabs[e];
            if (!String(r).startsWith("win_"))
              if (n < t.maxShown || 0 == t.maxShown) t.shownTabs.push(r), n++;
              else if (r == t.currentTabId || t.pinnedTabs[r]) {
                var s = t.shownTabs.filter(function (e) {
                  return e != t.currentTabId && !t.pinnedTabs[e];
                });

          t.tabs.push(e);
        },

            return t == e;

    ns.state;
    var rs = {
      namespaced: !0,
      state: { count: 0, status: "done" },
      mutations: {
        SET_STATUS: function (t, e) {
          if ("preparing" === e) t.count++;
          else if ("ready" === e)
            return t.count--, void (t.count <= 0 && (t.status = e));
          t.status = e;
        },
      },
      actions: {
        setStatus: function (t, e) {
          var n = t.commit;

        getStatus: function (t) {
          return t.status;
        },
      },
    };
    function ss(t, e, n, r) {
      if (e == n) return t;
      for (
        var s = t.indexOf(e), i = t.indexOf(n), o = [], a = 0;
        a < t.length;
        a++
      )
        a != s &&
          ("after" == r
            ? (o.push(t[a]), a == i && o.push(t[s]))
            : (a == i && o.push(t[s]), o.push(t[a])));
      return o;
    }
    var is = {
        namespaced: !0,
        state: { showMefoPrinter: !1, sectionsToPrint: [] },
        mutations: {
          SET_SHOW_MEFO_PRINTER: function (t, e) {
            t.showMefoPrinter = e;
          },
          ADD_SEC_TO_PRINTER: function (t, e) {
            var n = t.sectionsToPrint,
              r = n.filter(function (t) {
                return t.id == e.id;
              })[0];
            r || (t.sectionsToPrint = [].concat(Object(Ve["a"])(n), [e]));
          },
          REMOVE_SEC_FROM_PRINTER: function (t, e) {
            var n = t.sectionsToPrint,
              r = n.filter(function (t) {
                return t.id == e.id;
              })[0],
              s = n.filter(function (t) {
                return t.id != e.id;
              });
            r && (t.sectionsToPrint = s);
          },
          PUSH_BACK: function (t, e) {
            var n = t.sectionsToPrint,
              r = n.indexOf(e);
            n.splice(r, 1), n.splice(r - 1, 0, e), (t.sectionsToPrint = n);
          },
          PUSH_NEXT: function (t, e) {
            var n = t.sectionsToPrint,
              r = n.indexOf(e);
            n.splice(r, 1), n.splice(r + 1, 0, e), (t.sectionsToPrint = n);
          },
          MOVE_BEFORE: function (t, e) {
            var n = e.sec,
              r = e.secDist,
              s = t.sectionsToPrint;
            (s = ss(s, n, r, "before")), (t.sectionsToPrint = s);
          },
          MOVE_AFTER: function (t, e) {
            var n = e.sec,
              r = e.secDist,
              s = t.sectionsToPrint;
            (s = ss(s, n, r, "after")), (t.sectionsToPrint = s);
          },
          EMPTY_SECTIONS: function (t, e) {
            t.sectionsToPrint = [];
          },
        },

          setShowMefoPrinter: function (t, e) {

            var n = t.commit;

            var n = t.commit;
            n("PUSH_NEXT", e);
          },
          pushBack: function (t, e) {
            var n = t.commit;
            n("PUSH_BACK", e);
          },
          moveBefore: function (t, e) {
            var n = t.commit;
            n("MOVE_BEFORE", e);
          },
          moveAfter: function (t, e) {
            var n = t.commit;
            n("MOVE_AFTER", e);
          },
          emptySections: function (t) {
            var e = t.commit;
            e("EMPTY_SECTIONS");
          },
        },

        DO_SORT: function (t, e) {
          if (e.startsWith("custom_")) {
            try {
              Ts.forEach(function (t) {
                t.sortValue = 9999;
              }),
                Ts.forEach(function (t, e, n) {
                  Is.forEach(function (r, s) {
                    var i = r.get(r.root, t.id);
                    i && 9999 == n[e].sortValue && (n[e].sortValue = s + 1);
                  });
                });
            } catch (ex) {
              console.error(ex.message);
            }
            Ts.sort(function (t, e) {
              var n = t,
                r = e;
              return n.sortValue < r.sortValue
                ? -1
                : n.sortValue > r.sortValue
                ? 1
                : n.nameSort < r.nameSort
                ? -1
                : n.nameSort > r.nameSort
                ? 1
                : -1;
            });
          } else
            switch (e) {
              case "ideal":
                Ts.sort(function (t, e) {
                  var n = t,
                    r = e;
                  return (
                    n.special && ((n = t.book), (r = e.book)),
                    n.fs.rate < r.fs.rate
                      ? -1
                      : n.fs.rate > r.fs.rate
                      ? 1
                      : n.fs.matches > r.fs.matches
                      ? -1
                      : n.fs.matches < r.fs.matches
                      ? 1
                      : n.fs.results > r.fs.results
                      ? -1
                      : n.fs.results < r.fs.results || n.nameSort > r.nameSort
                      ? 1
                      : (n.nameSort, r.nameSort, -1)
                  );
                });
                break;
              case "profile":
                Ts.sort(function (t, e) {
                  var n = t,
                    r = e;
                  return (
                    n.special && ((n = t.book), (r = e.book)),
                    n.dor > r.dor
                      ? 1
                      : n.dor < r.dor
                      ? -1
                      : n.nameSort > r.nameSort
                      ? 1
                      : (n.nameSort, r.nameSort, -1)
                  );
                });
                break;
              case "rate":
                Ts.sort(function (t, e) {
                  var n = t,
                    r = e;
                  return (
                    n.special && ((n = t.book), (r = e.book)),
                    n.fs.rate < r.fs.rate
                      ? -1
                      : n.fs.rate > r.fs.rate || n.nameSort > r.nameSort
                      ? 1
                      : (n.nameSort, r.nameSort, -1)
                  );
                });
                break;
              case "results":
                Ts.sort(function (t, e) {
                  var n = t,
                    r = e;
                  return (
                    n.special && ((n = t.book), (r = e.book)),
                    n.fs.results < r.fs.results
                      ? 1
                      : n.fs.results > r.fs.results
                      ? -1
                      : n.nameSort > r.nameSort
                      ? 1
                      : (n.nameSort, r.nameSort, -1)
                  );
                });
                break;
              case "book":
                Ts.sort(function (t, e) {
                  var n = t,
                    r = e;
                  if (
                    (n.special && ((n = t.book), (r = e.book)), n.name > r.name)
                  )
                    return 1;
                  if (n.name < r.name) return -1;
                  if (n.mainVolume > r.mainVolume) return 1;
                  if (n.mainVolume < r.mainVolume) return -1;

                    if (t.position > e.position) return 1;
                    if (t.position < e.position) return -1;

                  return n.position > r.position
                    ? 1
                    : n.position < r.position
                    ? -1
                    : n.mainAuthorName > r.mainAuthorName
                    ? 1
                    : -1;
                });
                break;
              case "author":
                Ts.sort(function (t, e) {
                  var n = t,
                    r = e;

                    n.special && ((n = t.book), (r = e.book)),
                    n.authorSort > r.authorSort
                      ? 1
                      : n.authorSort < r.authorSort
                      ? -1
                      : 0
                  );
                });
                break;
            }

      Ci = {

          return t.current
            ? t.current.next.length > 0
              ? t.current.next
              : t.current.parent.next
            : e["getFolders"];
        },

              ? t.currentSystem.next
              : t.currentSystem.parent.next
            : e["getSystemFolders"].next;

                ? t.current.title

              ? e.defaultBackupLocation

        },

            r = e.newKey,
            s = t.personalAdditions[n];

            s.keys.push(r);
        },

            r = e.keyId,
            s = t.personalAdditions[n];

            (s.keys = s.keys.filter(function (t) {
              return t.id != r;
            }));
        },

            r = e.editKey,
            s = t.personalAdditions[n];

            (s.keys = s.keys.map(function (t) {
              return t.id === r.id ? r : t;

    function a(t, e) {
      var n = Object.keys(t);
      if (Object.getOwnPropertySymbols) {
        var r = Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(t);
        e &&
          (r = r.filter(function (e) {
            return Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(t, e).enumerable;
          })),
          n.push.apply(n, r);
      }
      return n;
    }
    function c(t) {
      for (var e = 1; e < arguments.length; e++) {
        var n = null != arguments[e] ? arguments[e] : {};
        e % 2
          ? a(Object(n), !0).forEach(function (e) {
              Object(i["a"])(t, e, n[e]);
            })
          : Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors
          ? Object.defineProperties(t, Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors(n))
          : a(Object(n)).forEach(function (e) {
              Object.defineProperty(
                t,
                e,
                Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(n, e)
              );
            });

      return t;
    }
    var u = {
        data: function () {
          return {
            routeBackName: "settings",
            iconV: "3",
            insteadOf: "insteadOf",
            newTab: "newTab",
            utd: "utd",
            rtl: "rtl",
            left: "left",
            right: "right",
            compact: "compact",
            large: "large",
            bright: "bright",
            dark: "dark",
            archaic: "archaic",
            colors: { red: "red", blue: "#777", black: "#000" },
            showAdvanced: !1,
          };
        },
        computed: c(
          {},
          Object(o["c"])("userSetting", ["getUserDisplaySetting"]),
          {
            newTabMode: function () {
              var t = this.userSettings.settings.newTabMode;
              return !(!t || "1" != t);
            },
            heightGzirim: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.height_gzir
                ? this.userSettings.settings.height_gzir
                : "low";
            },
            fsResultsTrans: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.fsresult_color
                ? this.userSettings.settings.fsresult_color
                : 2;
            },
            getTextSize: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.textSize
                ? this.userSettings.settings.textSize
                : "compact";
            },
            getBookItemSize: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.bookItemSize
                ? this.userSettings.settings.bookItemSize
                : "large";
            },
            bookSelection: function () {
              return !(
                !this.userSettings.settings.book_selection_default ||
                1 != this.userSettings.settings.book_selection_default
              );
            },
            hideRightBarOnFullScreen: function () {
              return !(
                !this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_right_bar ||
                1 != this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_right_bar
              );
            },
            hideSearchBarOnFullScreen: function () {
              return !(
                !this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_search_bar ||
                1 != this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_search_bar
              );
            },
            hideTopBarOnFullScreen: function () {
              return !(
                !this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_top_bar ||
                1 != this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_top_bar
              );
            },
            imageQuality: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.imgQuality || "high";
            },
            showPagePreview: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.showPagePreview || "on";
            },
            pagePreviewType: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.pagePreviewType || "full";
            },
            previewSize: function () {
              return this.userSettings.settings.pagePreviewSize || "medium";
            },
          }
        ),
        methods: {
          resetDefault: function () {
            this.$store.dispatch("userSetting/setSubColor", {
              color1: "#c67f05",
              color2: "#7d5104",
            }),
              this.$store.dispatch("userSetting/setBackgroundColor", "bright"),
              this.$store.dispatch("userSetting/setTextSize", "compact"),
              this.userSettings.setSettings("newTabMode", "0"),
              this.userSettings.setSettings("height_gzir", "low"),
              this.userSettings.setSettings("book_selection_default", "0"),
              this.userSettings.setSettings("full_screen_hide_right_bar", "0"),
              this.userSettings.setSettings("full_screen_hide_search_bar", "0"),
              this.userSettings.setSettings("full_screen_hide_top_bar", "0");
          },

      function A(t, e, n, r, s) {
        try {

            o = r.width / t;

    function w(t, e) {
      var n = Object.keys(t);
      if (Object.getOwnPropertySymbols) {
        var r = Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(t);
        e &&
          (r = r.filter(function (e) {
            return Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(t, e).enumerable;
          })),
          n.push.apply(n, r);
      }
      return n;
    }
    function S(t) {
      for (var e = 1; e < arguments.length; e++) {
        var n = null != arguments[e] ? arguments[e] : {};
        e % 2
          ? w(Object(n), !0).forEach(function (e) {
              Object(o["a"])(t, e, n[e]);
            })
          : Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors
          ? Object.defineProperties(t, Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors(n))
          : w(Object(n)).forEach(function (e) {
              Object.defineProperty(
                t,
                e,
                Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(n, e)
              );
            });

      return t;

    var O = {
        props: ["book", "gzirHeight", "words", "gzirIndex", "bookIndex"],
        data: function () {
          return {
            fullImage: !1,
            img: "",
            page: 0,
            pageId: "",
            coords: [],
            showSpinner: !1,
            hide: !1,
            gzirTop: 0,
          };
        },
        computed: S({}, Object(b["d"])("tabsManager", ["resizeToggle"]), {
          isActive: function () {
            var t =
              this.bookIndex.toString() + "." + (this.gzirIndex + 1).toString();
            return this.$store.state.currentActiveListIndex.toString() === t;
          },
        }),
        watch: {
          resizeToggle: function (t, e) {
            this.setCanvasSize(), this.draw();
          },
          gzirHeight: function (t, e) {
            this.doGzir();
          },
        },
        methods: {
          openResultInBook: function () {
            var t =
              this.bookIndex.toString() + "." + (this.gzirIndex + 1).toString();
            (this.$store.state.currentActiveListIndex = t),
              this.$emit("openbook", this.page);
          },
          toggleFullImage: function () {
            this.fullImage = !this.fullImage;
            var t = this.$refs.image;
            if (this.fullImage) {
              var e = this.img.width,
                n = this.img.height,
                r = (this.img.picture, t.width / e),
                s = n * r;
              t.height = s;
            } else t.height = this.gzirHeight;
            this.draw();
          },
          getCropRect: function (t) {
            try {
              var e = 100,
                n = [{ top: 100 }];
              try {
                n = this.coords.reduce(function (t, e) {
                  return t.top > e.top ? t : e;
                });
              } catch (ex) {}
              return (
                (this.gzirTop = n[0].top - e < 0 ? 0 : n[0].top - e),
                {
                  x: 0,
                  y: this.gzirTop,
                  w: 0,
                  h:
                    100 === this.gzirHeight
                      ? 0.2
                      : 100 === this.gzirHeight
                      ? 0.3
                      : 0.4,
                }
              );
            } catch (ex) {
              return { x: 0, y: 0, w: 0, h: 0 };
            }
          },
          draw: function () {
            if ("" != this.img) {
              try {
                this.coords.reduce(function (t, e) {
                  return t.top > e.top ? t : e;
                });
              } catch (ex) {}
              var t = this.$refs.image;
              if (void 0 != t) {
                var e = t.getContext("2d"),
                  n = this.img.picture,
                  r = this.img.imageMetaData,
                  s = r.width && 0 != r.width ? r.width : this.img.width,
                  i = r.height && 0 != r.height ? r.height : this.img.height,
                  o = r.top,
                  a = t.width / s,
                  c = i * a,
                  u = (t.height / c) * i;
                e.clearRect(0, 0, t.width, t.height),
                  e.drawImage(n, 0, 0, n.width, u, 0, 0, t.width, t.height);
                var l = r.PDF || this.img.webP;
                l &&
                  ((i *= 3e3 / s),
                  (s = 3e3),
                  (a = t.width / s),
                  (c = i * a),
                  c / i),
                  (e.globalCompositeOperation = "multiply"),
                  this.coords.forEach(function (t) {
                    t.forEach(function (t) {
                      (e.fillStyle = "rgba(255,255,0)"),
                        e.fillRect(
                          t.left * a,
                          (t.top - o) * a,
                          t.width * a,
                          t.height * a
                        );
                    });
                  });
              }
            }
          },
          setCanvasSize: function () {
            if (void 0 != this.$refs.container) {
              var t = this.$refs.image,
                e = this.$refs.container;
              return (
                (t.width = e.clientWidth), (t.height = this.gzirHeight), t.width
              );
            }
          },

                !this.showBookVolumes &&
                !this.isFs &&
                !this.typefree &&
                this.isClose
              );
            },

              return !0 === this.closeVol || void 0 == this.closeVol;
            },

              return this.favoriteBooksById
                ? this.$t("tooltip.removeFavorites")
                : this.$t("tooltip.addFavorites");
            },

              var t =
                (this.searchMode && 2 === this.$store.state.lastActiveList) ||
                (!this.searchMode && 1 === this.$store.state.lastActiveList);
              return (
                t &&
                this.$store.state.currentActiveListIndex ===
                  this.listIndex.toString()
              );
            },

              return this.active == this.book.id;

              return this.book.favorite;
            },

                "" != this.book.fs.fs

              var t = this,

                  (1 << n) & t.book.permissions && (e = !0);
                }),
                e

              return "free" == this.type;

                ? this.book.volume.substr(this.book.volume.indexOf(">") + 1)
                : this.book.volume;
            },

            },

    var J = {
        mainVolume: { onEmpty: null, bit: 0 },
        position: { onEmpty: null, bit: 1 },
        id: { onEmpty: null, bit: 2 },
        name: { onEmpty: "", bit: 3 },
        volume: { onEmpty: "", bit: 4 },
        authors_length: { onEmpty: 0, bit: 5 },
        permissions: { onEmpty: 0, bit: 6 },
        addnames_length: { onEmpty: 0, bit: 7 },
        places: { onEmpty: "", bit: 8 },
        toyear: { onEmpty: "", bit: 9 },
        fromyear: { onEmpty: "", bit: 10 },
        volumes_length: { onEmpty: 0, bit: 12 },
        moredata: { onEmpty: 0, bit: 13 },
      },
      tt = function (t) {
        var e = arguments.length > 1 && void 0 !== arguments[1] && arguments[1];
        if ("string" == typeof t) return t;
        var n = t;
        n = ~n;
        var r = 255 & n,
          s = n >> 8,
          i = F.substr(s, r);
        return e && (i = H.substr(s, r)), i;
      },
      et = {
        get: function (t, e, n) {
          var r = Reflect.get(t, "_bookinfo", n),
            s = J[e];
          if ("permissions" === e) return t["permissions"];
          if ("_show" === e) return 1 & r;
          if ("favorite" === e) return 8 & r;
          if ("_hide" === e) return 2 & r;
          if ("_inHide" === e) return 4 & r;
          if ("dor" === e) return 255 & t["moredata"];
          if ("isSidra" == e) return 512 & t["moredata"];
          if ("isText" == e) return 1024 & t["moredata"];
          if ("removed" == e) return 2048 & t["moredata"];
          if ("mainAuthorName" === e) {
            for (var i = t["authors_length"], o = [], a = 0; a < i; a++)
              if (1 == t["authors_" + a + "_authorTypeId"]) {
                var c = tt(t["authors_" + a + "_name"]);
                o.push(c);
              }
            return o.join(" - ");
          }
          if ("mainAuthorId" === e) {
            for (var u = t["authors_length"], l = [], d = 0; d < u; d++)
              if (1 == t["authors_" + d + "_authorTypeId"]) {
                var h = t["authors_" + d + "_id"];
                l.push(h);
              }
            return l;
          }
          if ("subBooks" === e) {
            for (var f = t["subbooks_length"], p = {}, m = 0; m < f; m++)
              p[t["subbooks_" + m + "_id"]] = {
                name: t["subbooks_" + m + "_name"],
                author: t["subbooks_" + m + "_author"],
                dor: t["subbooks_" + m + "_dor"],
              };
            return p;
          }
          if (s && !O.getBit(t._flag, s.bit)) return s.onEmpty;
          var g = Reflect.get(t, e, n);
          return g < 0 ? tt(g) : g;
        },
        set: function (t, e, n, r) {
          var s = Reflect.get(t, "_bookinfo", r),
            i = n;
          return "_show" === e
            ? ((i = n ? rt(s, 0) : nt(s, 0)), Reflect.set(t, "_bookinfo", i, r))
            : "favorite" === e
            ? ((i = n ? rt(s, 3) : nt(s, 3)), Reflect.set(t, "_bookinfo", i, r))
            : "_hide" === e
            ? ((i = n ? rt(s, 1) : nt(s, 1)), Reflect.set(t, "_bookinfo", i, r))
            : "_inHide" === e
            ? ((i = n ? rt(s, 2) : nt(s, 2)), Reflect.set(t, "_bookinfo", i, r))
            : Reflect.set(t, e, n, r);
        },
      };
    function nt(t, e) {
      var n = ~(1 << e);
      return t & n;
    }
    function rt(t, e) {
      return t | (1 << e);
    }
    function st() {}

    }

                  case 0:

              ((this.l = this.prevState.l),
              (this.t = this.prevState.t),

                      this.h + o > this.maxH &&

              !t.target.closest ||
              t.target.closest(".resizable-component") === this.$refs["parent"]

                }
          },
          handleUp: function () {
            if (0 !== this.resizeState) {
              (this.resizeState = 0), (document.body.style.cursor = "");
              var t = this.dragState ? "drag:end" : "resize:end";
              this.emitEvent(t), (this.dragState = !1);
            }
          },

          },

            this.reloadMefSections({

            var e = this;

              ? 1 == this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_right_bar &&
                this.toggleDockable(!1, !1, !1)
              : 1 != this.userSettings.settings.full_screen_hide_right_bar ||

                e.toggleSplitter();
              });
          },

          },

                this.$store.state.tabs[this.tabId].page,

              ));

          },

              (this.setSearching(!1),
              (this.$store.state.tabs[this.tabId].fsFinished = !1));

              );
          },

            (this.drawFs = !0),
              (this.$store.state.tabsManager.scrollToFsResult = !0);
          },

            this.txtBook && (this.currFsPage = t);
          },
          getCurrentPage: function (t) {
            this.scrollToPage(), this.scrollToTsiyun(), this.scrollToTsiyun2();
          },

              );

            tsiyunimType1: function () {
              var t = this;
              try {
                var e = this.filteredLists.tsiyunim
                  .filter(function (t) {
                    return 1 == t.type;
                  })
                  .map(function (e) {

                      position: t.getPageRealPosition(e.page),
                    });
                  });
                return e;
              } catch (ex) {

              }

            tsiyunimType2: function () {
              var t = this;
              try {
                var e = this.filteredLists.tsiyunim2
                  .filter(function (t) {
                    return 2 == t.type;
                  })
                  .map(function (e) {
                    return zr({}, e, {
                      name: t.getPageName(e.page),
                      position: t.getPageRealPosition(e.page),
                    });
                  });

                return [];
              }

            filteredLists2: function () {
              var t = this,
                e = this.searchTxt,
                n = this.getPages.filter(function (t) {
                  try {
                    return t.parentTitle.includes(e.pages) && 0 == t.subId;
                  } catch (ex) {
                    return console.error(ex), !1;
                  }
                }),
                r = this.getPages.filter(function (n) {
                  try {
                    return (
                      n.subTitle.includes(e.tsiyunim) &&
                      n.parentId == t.currentParent
                    );
                  } catch (ex) {
                    return !1;
                  }
                }),
                s = { mainPages: n, subPages: r };
              return s;
            },
            filteredLists: function () {
              var t = this.searchTxt,
                e = 1,
                n = this.getPages.map(function (t, e) {
                  return t.empty && (t.position = 0), t;
                });
              n.forEach(function (t) {
                t.position > 0 &&
                  (void 0 == t.originPosition &&
                    (t.originPosition = t.position),
                  (t.position = e),
                  e++);
              }),
                (n = n.filter(function (e) {
                  if ("" === t.pages) return e;
                  try {
                    return e.pagedata &&
                      "" != e.pagedata[0].letter &&
                      null != e.pagedata[0].letter
                      ? e.pagedata[0].letter.includes(t.pages)
                      : e.position.toString().includes(t.pages);
                  } catch (ex) {
                    return console.error(ex.message, ex), !1;
                  }
                }));
              var r = this.getTsiyunim.filter(function (e) {
                  try {
                    return e.title.includes(t.tsiyunim) && 1 == e.type;
                  } catch (ex) {
                    return console.error(ex.message, ex), !1;
                  }
                }),
                s = this.getTsiyunim.filter(function (e) {
                  try {
                    return e.title.includes(t.tsiyunim2) && 2 == e.type;
                  } catch (ex) {
                    return console.error(ex.message, ex), !1;
                  }
                }),
                i = this.getUserTsiyuns.filter(function (e) {
                  return e.title.includes(t.myTsiyunim);
                }),
                o = this.userCommentsList.filter(function (e) {
                  return e.data.includes(t.comment);
                }),
                a = this.userKeyList.filter(function (e) {
                  return e.value.includes(t.key);
                });
              this.totalMarkers = this.userMarkersList.length;
              var c = this.markers,
                u = this.userLinksList,
                l = {
                  pages: n,
                  tsiyunim: r,
                  userTsiyunim: i,
                  comment: o,
                  key: a,
                  marker: c,
                  links: u,
                  tsiyunim2: s,
                };

            getBookTabs: function () {

                (this.isSearching = n);
            },

              this.setSearching(!1);

                    );

            },
            toggleOCR: function (t) {
              var e = this,
                n = t.show,
                r = t.img,
                s = t.x,
                o = t.y,

                c = t.height,

              if (

                  ((this.tempCanvasCtx.fillStyle = "white"),
                  this.tempCanvasCtx.fillRect(
                    0,
                    0,
                    this.tempCanvas.width,
